Before creating the game make sure to divide the game into small parts. 

#step 1- create a snake body 
#step 2 - move the snake 
#step 3- control the snake
#step 4 - make the food and detect the collision with the food 
#step 5 - create a scoreboard 
#step 6 - detect collision with walls 
#step 7 - detect collision with its own tail 